imdb.plot outline: A compilation of the most high voltage sports created using extensive backyard action in Freestyle Motocross, Surfing, Skate, BMX, Mountain Bikes, Kite, Wake and Hot Babes. Hosted by world famous action-sports athletes Bushy, Alfy, and Krystal, this series profiles exclusive insider stories of secret surf breaks, hidden skate bowls, ultimate FMX compounds and includes behind the scenes interviews with the world's best extreme sports stars, like current world-record holder Robbie Maddison.
imdb.title: Home Grown Maniacs
